{"type": "article", "id": 25005, "title": "可漏水的餐盘", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-06T07:18:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607183914J7xizCN6YWH9fXM0.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个可以放餐具的盘子，它也有漏水的功能。盘子中间小山一样的圆锥是用来隔离餐具的，而四周的三角边可以嵌上餐盒或挂上杯子，成为一个小的收纳。盘子下面的四个支撑脚可以替换两种长短的脚垫，用来转换蓄水和倒水，当积累到一定程度时就可沿着出水口倒出。<a href=\"http://www.lakeland.co.uk/p24730/ILO-Clam-Shell-Dish-Drainers\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183912KTzGpdq7B8esMNLQ.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183912KCTIYlDv8U3H0dqP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183913Hx8TagyC6UsRNGZ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183913DGZBCwyMiHJTA45z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607183914krzuyYW8pK0VS1iQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}